Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:37.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now you thought
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:38.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you had me by the upper － hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:41.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}but I see through the face you've covered cynical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:41.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( FOUR )
