Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:48.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Without the fear and tears surrounding you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:49.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( ONE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:51.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because your soul is what you were BORN TO BE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:55.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たとえ今まで生きるstrategy 夢失っても　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:22:56.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(It's time now)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:58.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ハンドルを切って暴れ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:01.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夢のまま突き進め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:03.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬のない人生に挑むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:06.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忍のない感情を抱くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:08.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覚悟決めて行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:11.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分自身をbreak away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.36,0:23:16.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全てを奪われる運命なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.17,0:23:18.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何を信じて生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:23.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ask yourself, the way there's nothing to live or die for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:26.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過去も傷も恐れるなら
